Google,Gmail,now,supports,the,standard,IMAP,and,SMTP,protocols,for,accessing,and,sending,e,mail,messages,The,Gmail,IMAP,and,SMTP,servers,have,been,extended,to,support,authorization,via,the,industry,standard,OAuth,protocol,This,allows,third,party,applications,to,access,a,user,s,email,account,with,their,permission